e":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"條女好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"仲等咩<br />\n<br />\n搭車上去屌爆佢個西啦<br />\n<br />\n屌完唔好返黎"},{"pid":"08b52ae6adddd4200e45b9d6677dc9bf6ccbbc92","tid":1853991,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0cc948d298dbc55e87d2568b00d653f369437f","tid":1853991,"uid":66202,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"4faf0fb88868e73711fcd20ae616df94446e1de1","tid":1853991,"uid":116021,"like":274,"dislike":0,"score":274,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"其實係咪慢慢爆 最後會發現真係p4實驗室流出武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"我諗係因為武漢p4實驗室爆煲泄漏化武所以美國出手調查近排頻頻拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqXb0P.gif&h=31e53dd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"828e2e1cbdc55772460d7b64a73d4103170966c1","tid":1853991,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30266704397eee0df1f27740a807cb9ff7519f08","tid":1853991,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:57:06.000Z","msg":"真係外國勢力"},{"pid":"1a5a0e73f397e4385e4ee55f47e7bbd873412e36","tid":1853991,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},{"pid":"240324b43575a1023d713152724f4c8670c7babb","tid":1853991,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e61ba320df9bac3f612515732c48dc09285f4c99","tid":1853991,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/01/31/phpCs879B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F01%2F31%2FphpCs879B.jpg&h=f295f1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-01-31 14:16:59<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國檢方28日起訴3名參與中國「千人計畫」學者，其中一人為波士頓大學研究人員葉艷卿（Yanqing Ye，譯音），由於美方認定葉人在中國，聯邦調查局（FBI）遂在近日發布通緝令，同時揭露她的身分，為中國人民解放軍中尉。<br />\n<br />\nFBI近日正式對葉艷卿發布通緝令，據資料顯示，葉為1990年7月22日於福建省出生，不到30歲相當年輕，並附上兩張大頭照供外界辨認。內容寫道，葉艷卿是中國解放軍中尉，亦是中國共產黨黨員，就讀中國人民解放軍國防科技大學，判斷人已回到中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉艷卿被指控偽造學生身分，同時隱瞞解放軍軍職，在美期間與國防科大長官、同事保持密切聯繫。在2017年10月至2019年4月，於波士頓大學研究物理、化學、生物醫學工程時，仍持續從事解放軍工作，並完成數件軍方指派的任務，包括評估美軍方網站及傳送美方文件、資訊回中國。<br />\n<br />\n另外2人分別為美國哈佛大學化學與化學生物系系主任李柏（Charles Leiber）和波士頓大學研究員鄭灶松（Zaosong Zheng，譯音），調查指出，李柏每月接受武漢理工大學提供5萬美元與多達15萬8000美元的生活津貼，並在武漢理大成立一座實驗室，代價為每年至少9個月為武漢理大工作；鄭灶松則被控企圖將敏感生物樣本夾帶走私回中國，以便繼續研究。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"回國後整容"},{"pid":"a1b8b644db85a0734ed7ea01388745e09f0c5ff0","tid":1853991,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a5a0e73f397e4385e4ee55f47e7bbd873412e36","tid":1853991,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/counterintelligence/yanqing-ye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fwanted%2Fcounterintelligence%2Fyanqing-ye&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=fbfa324a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/counterintelligence/yanqing-ye</a>"},{"pid":"662848fdbdc2cc54e69c0a7675040d25ac8efe77","tid":1853991,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c046e4d655400370e6afe452d71974204697afb","tid":1853991,"uid":22719,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"3a157f